    "comment": "<div style=\"font-size:0.9285rem\"><div>Hi&nbsp;zp[@zpuser#898913996#Garry Caber]zp,<br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Please see feedback from the client below:<br/></div><ol dir=\"ltr\"><li>General remarks<br/></li><ul><li>Change verbiage, do not mention Shanna's name. Use &quot;we&quot; or &quot;our team&quot; - apply in app and emails<br/></li></ul><li>How would you like to get started?<br/></li><ul><li>Both Free Consultation Call and Request a proposal are for new clients<br/></li><li>Change &quot;I received a proposal&quot; to &quot;Ask for a proposal&quot;<br/></li><li>Ask for a proposal should lead to a page with a short form (Name, Address, Email, Contact number, Primary concern) - purely for inquiry<br/></li></ul><li>Free Consultation Call<br/></li><ul><li>Primary concern - change to a text box, not a dropdown<br/></li><li>Remove bottom text field<br/></li><li>Shanna would like this to be a video call. As much as possible, therapists should not contact the client outside of the app<br/></li></ul><li>Send proposal<br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>For the services, make it a checkbox for each service - admin can select multiple services for the client<br/></li><li>In the PDF, please fix the overlapping content bugs<br/></li><li>For the Send Custom Email, can we set it to choose Zoho Mail as default?<br/></li></ol><li>Intake Form<br/></li><ul><li>Please follow the fields from their provided file.<br/></li><li>When adding a profile photo, there is an error in submitting.<br/></li></ul><li>Client Pool<br/></li><ul><li>In this client pool, therapists can choose which ones to take.<br/></li><li>Let's create a prompt for clients that are not taken within 2 days. This should notify the admin so she can coordinate with the therapists.<br/></li></ul><li>Payment Confirmed Email<br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>Currently, this gets sent when there is already a therapist assigned. Can we do this even before then?<br/></li><li>This doesn't include the invoice attached as well. Please recheck.<br/></li></ol><li><span>Packaged sessions</span><br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>Client and therapist should set these schedules ahead<br/></li></ol><li>Session reminders<br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>Is this in place already?<br/></li></ol><li>Business Details<br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>Change to &quot;Elodi Online Therapy and Learning Center&quot; everywhere<br/></li><li>Can we create a logo for this based on the brand colors and business scope?<br/></li></ol><li>Session Room<br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>I encountered a bug when I joined the room and agreed to the recording, it logged me out. Might be a one-time thing but best to check as well.<br/></li><li>Therapist should also have an option to pause the recording<br/></li><li>Add in the 5-minutes notice when the session is about to end<br/></li><li>The session should be ended manually by the therapist. This will allow them an allowance for extension.<br/></li><li>Can we add another column for notes aside from the chat box?<br/></li></ol><li>Release Report<br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>This is for the Evaluation Report. Make sure these are just text boxes that therapists will have to input their findings. Please refer to the file attached.<br/></li></ol><li>Existing clients<br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>Shanna has existing clients that she would like to bring to the app for additional testing. How do we bypass the steps? Can we just add their emails directly?<br/></li></ol><li>Payment<br/></li><ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><li>Right now, the &quot;pay first before session&quot; rule is not a priority. She can do manual for now in the testing phase. Clients can pay after the session or within the week.<br/></li></ol></ol><div><br/></div><div>Please let me know if you have any questions. Thank you!<br/></div><div><br/></div></div>",
